{"tid":374673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兩次換肝仍難逃離死神 鄧桂思今凌晨病逝","createTime":"2017-08-26T02:55:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-26T02:56:57.000Z","uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"281a2e758a9431320a85f3773af433d28894ce13","tid":374673,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T02:55:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170826&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=57074255\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170826%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D57074255&d=yrJc84O7XcVjWbJJagXf9rIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=3f0dffbb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170826%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D57074255&h=9991e292\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170826&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=57074255</a><br />\n<br />\n據悉，兩度進行換肝手術的鄧桂思留醫多時，病情近日急轉直下，延至26日凌晨不治。自鄧桂思進行兩度肝臟移手術後，整體情況一直未如理想，雖然新換的肝臟可運作，但感染了屬於真菌的念珠菌；因其肺部也感染念珠菌，所以要用人工肺維持生命。至今她使用人工肺最少110日，期間完全依賴人工肺為生，一直情況危殆，需留在深切治療部留醫，期間多名換肝病人也康復出院。"},{"pid":"9f55c0efa3f9cba000df3bd720274eb1353b2f75","tid":374673,"uid":82398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T02:56:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 辛苦左成大半年"}]}